title: Kubernetes component status
agents: linux
catalog: app/kubernetes
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the components of a kubernetes cluster.
 If a component is not healthy the check returns {CRIT} otherwise {OK}.
 If the status of a component is unknown the check returns {UNKNOWN}.

inventory:
 One service per component is created.

item:
 The name of the component.